Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.00,0:01:32.15,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}超体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.43,0:03:08.20,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}露西
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.11,0:30:57.31,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我的腿!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.90,0:48:43.66,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我接到一个美国公民从台湾打来的奇怪电话
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.66,0:48:47.39,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一个年轻女子给我们提供了大型贩毒团伙信息
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.39,0:48:49.44,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 我来处理   - 好的 交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.10,0:50:08.35,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.68,0:50:18.88,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.14,0:50:21.44,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}德国 柏林
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.46,0:50:22.57,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.24,0:50:31.96,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是他! 抓住他!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.95,0:50:42.53,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}请跟我走一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.95,0:50:54.93,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}法国 巴黎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.31,0:51:03.40,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.21,0:51:06.18,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}先生 跟我走一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.33,0:51:18.20,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}意大利 罗马
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.33,0:51:24.20,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}欢迎来到罗马
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.06,0:51:33.57,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}早上好 先生
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.61,0:51:36.24,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你好 跟我过来 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.30,0:52:07.49,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好的 三个都抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.90,0:55:18.65,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}她小腹有伤疤?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.65,0:55:20.97,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的 是我们给她取出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.07,0:55:23.43,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 她还好吗?  - 很好 她没事
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.43,0:55:26.11,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我给她注射了一针 她一天内会醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.49,0:56:11.26,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 医生 她醒了  - 你确定?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.45,0:56:12.96,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的 她坐在床上
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.88,0:56:18.93,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就是她
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.94,0:56:21.16,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 你没铐住她?  - 必须有啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.34,0:57:22.64,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}别把车放那里 停好了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.83,0:58:54.04,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}伙计们 进去!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.24,0:59:03.86,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}和警察说去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.15,0:59:08.56,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我看着手术
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.65,0:59:11.19,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 去弄点吃的来  - 你这个吃货
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.02,1:02:18.34,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}嘿 我给你买了...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.40,1:03:01.26,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}杀了她 拿到毒品
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.83,1:03:20.94,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}别傻站着 杀了她!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.73,1:05:37.71,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}跟上那辆车
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.55,1:07:28.96,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}老大 我们有五个人死在医院 对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.90,1:07:31.75,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}还剩多少人手?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.75,1:07:34.27,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我这边还有二十五人
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.55,1:07:37.44,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}该死的 她真顽强 她是个巫婆
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.98,1:07:42.66,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我知道
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.74,1:07:46.08,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我要亲手杀了她
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.02,1:10:08.01,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}给我搜整个大楼 找到她!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.06,1:13:53.97,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}冲俊!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.03,1:13:55.64,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我在这里 老大!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.73,1:13:57.41,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}干掉他们
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.46,1:13:59.13,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好的 老大!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.70,1:14:02.12,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你们 给我上
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.41,1:14:04.47,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好了吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.48,1:14:07.51,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你还好吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.80,1:14:11.49,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}快找医生 快!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.47,1:20:53.65,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}她呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.89,1:20:59.43,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}她人呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.74,1:21:00.68,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}回答我!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.71,1:21:03.03,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}回答我!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.97,1:22:02.96,英上中下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我无处不在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.52,0:01:51.12,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Life was given to us a billion years ago.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}十亿年前 我们被赐予了生命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.24,0:01:53.92,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,What have we done with it?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们用它做了什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.57,0:02:12.47,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}露西?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.00,0:02:15.99,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as easy as pie. In and out, all done and dusted.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就小事一桩 进去就出来 一切都准备就绪了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.09,0:02:17.33,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't do it yourself?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那你为什么不自己去办?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.33,0:02:21.18,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,The last thing the guy is expecting is a total 10 turning up to deliver the case.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那家伙绝对想不到会有个大美女来给他送手提箱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:22.99,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll blow his mind. Come on.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你会让他大吃一惊的 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.17,0:02:24.30,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,What's in it?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这里面是什么东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.43,0:02:26.08,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweetheart...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}小甜心...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.42,0:02:29.69,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get paranoid on me, alright? You trust me, don't you?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}别疑神疑鬼的好吗? 你相信我 不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.75,0:02:42.23,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Richard, I really do like you but...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}理查德 我是很喜欢你 可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.03,0:02:45.64,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I've to take care of myself right now, I got a...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我现在得先照顾好自己 我有个...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.07,0:02:48.89,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, I gotta concentrate on so many things.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我也不知道 我有好多事得操心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:51.19,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey! What are you doing?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}嘿! 嘿! 你上哪去?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.19,0:02:53.50,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home because I have exams on Monday.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我回家啊 星期一我有考试
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.51,0:02:56.66,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to shower and I have to study, OK?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我得洗个澡 还得复习 好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.66,0:03:00.31,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what? The other day I was in this museum and you know what I found out?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你知道吗? 前几天我在博物馆里的时候学到了什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:01.46,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,What?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.52,0:03:03.81,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,The first ever woman was named Lucy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}世上第一个女人的名字就叫露西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.67,0:03:10.11,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that suppose to make me feel better?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你以为这能让我心情好一点吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.31,0:03:11.57,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:14.46,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- No.  - I'll call you, OK?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 不是  - 我会联络你的 好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:15.86,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,OK! OK! OK!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}行! 行! 行!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:19.80,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be honest with you. I can't deliver the case myself.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我跟你说实话吧 我没法亲自送箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:22.42,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I've a little falling out with the guy. It's nothing major...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我和这家伙之前谈崩了 不是什么大事...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.58,0:03:24.78,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,but if it's you, problem solved.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}可是要是你送的话 问题就解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.07,0:03:27.51,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,You walk in there, you go up to the reception,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你走进去 到前台
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.51,0:03:29.63,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,you ask Mr. Jang to come down.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}让他叫张先生下来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.63,0:03:33.36,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,He comes down, he takes the case, you flash him your prettiest smile and bounce.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他下来 拿走手提箱 你给他闪个你最迷人的笑容 然后走人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:38.58,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, you can even see the reception from here.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你看 前台从这里都能看得见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.25,0:03:40.58,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.81,0:03:43.65,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- What's in the case?  - I don't know, it's just some paperwork.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 箱子里到底是什么?  - 不知道 就一堆文件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.80,0:03:46.33,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yeah? Let's see it then.  - It's locked\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 是吗? 那让咱看看  - 锁着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:48.14,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,and no one but Mr. Jang has the code.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}除了张先生以外没人有密码
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.89,0:03:50.41,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just the delivery boy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我就是个送信人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.51,0:03:53.00,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- Do you get paid to do this?  - Yeah, kinda.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 你这么做有钱赚吗?  - 啊 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.03,0:03:54.35,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Like how much?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}大概给多少?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.74,0:03:57.64,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, we're negotiating now or ...?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}现在是在谈价钱了还是...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.64,0:04:00.18,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, how much do you get paid? I want to know, how much?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不是 不是 你能赚多钱? 我想知道 多少?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.06,0:04:02.44,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,A thousand dollars.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一千美元
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:06.42,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,You get paid a thousand dollars for delivering paperwork, really?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}给你一千美金让你送点文件 真的假的?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.42,0:04:10.47,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, it takes me 10 minutes and they're paying a grand and the rest is none of my business.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不知道 总之只用我十分钟 他们就付我一千块 剩下的不关我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.47,0:04:12.13,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not my business either. I'll tell you now...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好啊 也不关我什么事 我跟你说...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.13,0:04:13.44,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- Listen!  - What?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 听我说!  - 干嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.64,0:04:16.36,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,We split it down the middle.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们五五平分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.68,0:04:19.53,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,That's 500 for you and 500 for me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你五百 我五百
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:23.04,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- Richard, I will call you.  - Listen! It is the third time this week\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 理查德 我会打电话给你的  - 听我说! 这礼拜我已经三次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.05,0:04:26.61,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm showing up at the same hotel with the same cowboy hat.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}出现在同一个酒店 戴着同一顶牛仔帽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.64,0:04:29.33,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Problem solved.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}问题解决啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.48,0:04:31.72,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- Go! Go! I'll wait for you to go.  - Lucy, honey,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 去吧! 去吧! 我会等着你的  - 露西 宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.86,0:04:33.94,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I've done this a dozen times.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我... 这活我已经做过十几次了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.13,0:04:38.03,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,It's paperwork! It's probably just some designs they swept so they can copy them.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}只是文件! 可能就是他们为了仿造而偷来的一些设计图
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:39.31,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it works in this country.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这国家就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.37,0:04:41.35,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Even my Stetson was made here. Look!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就连我的斯泰森牛仔帽也是从这产的 你看!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.53,0:04:44.02,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,It says so on the label: "Made in Taiwan"\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}标签上写着呢: "台湾制造"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:48.68,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,So long, cowboy, with a fake Stetson.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}再会了 戴着冒牌斯泰森牛仔帽的牛仔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:49.56,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Baby, please!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}宝贝 求你了!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.62,0:04:50.81,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Richard, I gotta go.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}理查德 我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:53.19,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- What the hell are you doing?  - I'm sorry.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 你干嘛呢?  - 很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.19,0:04:55.80,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- What the hell are you do...  - I'm so sorry. I really need your help.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 你到底干...  - 非常抱歉 我是真的需要你的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.80,0:04:58.32,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Stop it! Take this off me, right now!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}打住! 打住! 马上给我摘下来!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.32,0:04:59.57,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- I can't!  - Take this off me, right now!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 我没办法!  - 马上给我摘下来!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.58,0:05:01.90,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- I can't! Mr. Jang is the only one who has the key!  - No!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 我没办法! 张先生是唯一有钥匙的人!  - 不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.91,0:05:03.85,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,All you have to is go into the hotel and ask for him at the reception.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你只需要走进酒店里面 跟前台说你要找他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.85,0:05:05.10,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Take it off me, right now!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不行! 马上给我摘下来!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:08.32,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry, I really have no choice. The sooner you go in, the sooner you'll be back out.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}真对不起 我真的别无选择 你越快进去就越快出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.42,0:05:10.32,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you did this to me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我真不敢相信你会这么对我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.32,0:05:13.89,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- I'll be right here, you have my word.  - Your word isn't worth shit!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 我在这一动不动 我向你保证  - 你的保证连个屁都不值!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.11,0:05:16.86,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... it's worth 500 bucks, upfront.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}呃... 值五百块 提前支付
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.22,0:05:18.33,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an asshole!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你真是个王八蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.40,0:05:19.55,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're wonderful, huh?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你真是棒极了 对不?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.68,0:05:40.24,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, may I help you?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}小姐 我能为你效劳吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.29,0:05:42.38,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.71,0:05:46.42,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here for, uh...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我想要找 呃...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:48.63,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Jang.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}张先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.75,0:05:50.90,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:05:59.78,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Who should I say is here?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我应该说是谁要找他?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.97,0:06:01.87,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Richard.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}理查德
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:05.48,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhm... no... Richard sent... Richard sent me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}呃... 不对... 理查德叫我... 理查德叫我来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:11.40,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,What is your name?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你叫什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.02,0:06:13.54,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Richard.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不是 是理查德
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.71,0:06:18.42,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Richard's... uh... he's just looking for a place to park.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}理查德... 呃... 他在找停车位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.02,0:06:27.68,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Jang still wants to know your name.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}张先生还是想知道你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:32.13,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}露西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.23,0:06:33.76,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy what?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}露西什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.94,0:06:38.60,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Just Lucy. If he could... If he could he quick 'cause I have... I have to...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就是露西 他要是能... 要是能快点的话 因为我得... 我得...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.67,0:06:39.78,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a second while I translate...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}先等我翻译一下...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:49.55,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Jang is on his way, stay right here.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}张先生马上下来 待在这别动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.66,0:06:51.63,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I sit?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我能坐下吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.73,0:06:56.44,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Jang said you need to stay right here. I think it's better if you stay right here.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}张先生让你待在这别动 我觉得你最好待在这别动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.13,0:06:59.61,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me. Regent Hotel.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不好意思 皇家酒店
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:21.48,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,No!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.19,0:07:34.23,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,No!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.77,0:07:37.60,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait! No!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不要 等等! 不要啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.41,0:07:42.55,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}求你们了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.68,0:07:52.70,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I don't know anything!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}等一下 我什么都不知道!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:56.10,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything! Please! Please!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我什么都不知道! 求求你! 求求你!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:27.21,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,No, please!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不要 求求你!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.11,0:09:06.65,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you speak English?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}您会说英语吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:14.28,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Tambien hablo poco Espanol.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我也会说一点西班牙语
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.48,0:09:32.17,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, yes, I'm Lucy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}露西 对 我是露西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:35.79,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just been a terrible mistake. I'm just suppose to deliver this case.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}其实就是天大的误解 我只是来送这个手提箱的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.73,0:09:41.46,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,If you lost the key, you don't have to chop off my hand, you can just cut the chain, OK?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}您钥匙要是丢了 不需要切我的手 切锁链就行 好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:45.07,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}求求你!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.26,0:09:47.68,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you, please!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我求您了 拜托了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.53,0:09:53.42,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No! No!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不要! 不要! 不要呀!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:57.51,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No! Please!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不要! 不要! 求求你!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:10:00.24,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}求求你!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:01.45,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}求求你!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.70,0:10:17.48,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Miss, I speak English. I translate for Mr. Jang.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}小姐您好 我会说英语 我为张先生做翻译
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:31.04,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell him that I haven't done anything. I don't know anything.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}请你告诉他 我什么都没做 我什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:35.49,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all just a big mistake, OK? Please, please tell him that.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这整个就是个天大的误解 好吗? 请你跟他说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.49,0:10:37.50,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, OK, OK, hold on.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好 可以 稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.34,0:10:49.00,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Jang wants to know what's in the case.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}张先生想知道箱子里装的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.01,0:10:52.49,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't know what's in the case. Do you speak English or don't you speak English?!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不知道里面是什么 你到底会不会说英语?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.49,0:10:56.72,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I do! I studied one year at International High School in New York.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我会! 我在纽约的一所国际高中里读过一年书
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:10:57.87,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,OK.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.33,0:11:03.14,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Richard gave me the case to give to you, that's all I know.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}理查德让我把这个箱子给你 我只知道这些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.14,0:11:04.91,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, please tell him that.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好 请你告诉他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.60,0:11:34.67,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,He gave me a paper with numbers written on it, I don't... what is this?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他给了我一张写了数字的纸 我不... 这是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.76,0:11:37.11,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the code to open the case.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是开箱的密码
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.37,0:11:44.93,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,What's really in here?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这里面究竟是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:46.55,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing dangerous.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不是危险的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:50.66,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,So why won't he open it himself?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那他怎么不自己开?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:11:57.84,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't trust Mr. Richard.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他不信任理查德先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.33,0:12:00.29,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't trust Richard either.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我也不信任理查德
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.44,0:12:02.62,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I only dated him for a week.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我只和他谈了一星期的恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.96,0:12:10.60,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,OK! OK! OK!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}行! 行! 行!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.63,0:12:13.87,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- Mr. Jang insists that you open the case.  - OK! OK!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 张先生执意要你打开箱子  - 行! 行!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.41,0:12:21.00,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Please God, help me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}上帝啊 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:33.00,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,He wants you to hurry up, Mr. Jang has other things to do.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他让你利索点 张先生还有要事缠身
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:07.60,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you describe the content of the case?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你可不可以描述一下箱子里的东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.60,0:13:11.83,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,It's 4 plastic pouches filled with blue powder like a...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是四个塑料袋 里面装着蓝色的粉末像是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.83,0:13:15.02,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,or maybe a purple powder? I don't know, it looks gross.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}或许是紫色的粉末? 我不知道 看起来挺恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.04,0:15:37.86,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Jang wants to offer you a job.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}张先生想给你一份工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.76,0:15:41.01,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,A job?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}工作?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.72,0:15:46.25,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want a job!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不想要工作!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.99,0:15:52.09,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,If life starts approximately a billion years ago,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}生命起源于大约十亿年前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.10,0:15:54.49,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll have to wait 400,000 years\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们得在四十万年后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.50,0:15:57.56,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,to see the aberration of the first nerve cells.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}才能看到第一波神经细胞演变出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.17,0:16:00.64,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where life we know it begins.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这就是我们说的生命的起点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.65,0:16:04.24,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Brains in formation of only a few milligrams\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}从这些只有几毫米长的脑组织中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:09.35,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,is not possible to determine any sign of intelligence yet.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们无法断定 是否有智慧的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.63,0:16:11.91,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,It acts more as a reflex.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}它表现得更像反射作用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.29,0:16:17.70,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,One neuron, you're alive. Two neurons, you're moving.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一颗脑细胞 你活着 两颗脑细胞 你动着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.86,0:16:21.55,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,And with movement, interesting things begin to happen.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}而一旦有了活动 就会出现有趣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.76,0:16:30.53,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Animal life on Earth goes back millions of years.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}数百万年前地球上就出现了动物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.73,0:16:36.00,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, most species only use 3-5% of its cerebral capacity.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}然而 大多数物种只使用了大脑的百分之三到五
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.00,0:16:40.90,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,But it isn't until we reached human beings at the top of the animal chain,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}可是 只有成为人类 达食物链顶端的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:45.68,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,that we finally see a species used more of its cerebral capacity.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们才终于发现一种物种更多地使用了其脑容量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:53.38,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,10% may not seem like much but it's a lot if we look at all we've done with it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}百分之十看似不多 但要是从人类用它所做的一切来看 已经很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.38,0:17:29.73,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's discuss a special case.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}现在我们来谈论一个特例
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.83,0:17:35.33,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,The only living being that uses its brain better than us...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}唯一一种比我们更好地利用大脑的生物...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.57,0:17:36.76,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,the dolphin.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}海豚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:41.42,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,It's estimated that this incredible animal\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}据估计 这种不可思议的动物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.50,0:17:45.80,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,uses up to 20% of its cerebral capacity.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}可以利用到大脑的百分之二十
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.81,0:17:52.39,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,And in particular, this allows it to have an echo-location system\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}尤其在于 这使它拥有着一种回声定位系统
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.39,0:17:57.11,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,that's more efficient than any sonar invented by mankind.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}比任何人类所发明的声纳系统都更加有效
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.12,0:18:01.74,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,But the dolphin did not invent the sonar. It developed it naturally.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但是海豚并没有发明声纳 它是自然形成的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.84,0:18:06.04,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is the crucial part of our\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}而这就是我们今天的哲学探讨中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.28,0:18:09.10,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,philosophical reflection we have today.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}最具有关键性的环节
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:11.14,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we therefore conclude\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们是否能够得出这样的结论
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.14,0:18:14.54,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,that humans are concerned more with\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}即人类更在意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.85,0:18:16.27,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,"having"\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}"拥有"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.88,0:18:18.34,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,than "being".\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}而不是"具有"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.86,0:19:17.37,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}露西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.64,0:19:19.99,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do with my stomach?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你对我的腹部做了些什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.91,0:19:25.19,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing! Just a little horizontal slit. It's very well done\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没什么! 只是一个小小的水平切口 刀工非常利落
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.20,0:19:29.78,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,and you'll find that in a month, this scar is practically invisible too.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一个月之后你会看到 疤痕基本就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.65,0:19:33.59,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be able to show your tummy off on the beach next summer.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}明年夏天你就能去海滩秀你的小蛮腰了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:35.72,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about the scar.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不在乎有没有疤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.95,0:19:40.26,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it, uh... is it why we opened you up?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是不是 呃... 是不是我们为什么给你开刀?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.73,0:19:44.87,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest assured, we didn't harvest your organs or anything.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你放心 我们没有取你的器官什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.87,0:19:48.72,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, we merely slipped a little package in your lower tummy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们只是在你小腹里面放了个小包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.77,0:19:52.70,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a... it's a new drug the kids in Europe are gonna love, believe me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}它是... 一种新毒品 欧洲的孩子们会爱上它的 相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.73,0:19:57.10,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- What is it?  - Well, the scientific term is CPH4,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 到底是什么?  - 学名叫做CPH4
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.23,0:19:59.76,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,which is not very sexy from a sale's point of view.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}从销售方面来看名字的确不是很诱人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:03.76,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,So, uh... we're... we're still working on something a little bit more pop...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}所以呃... 我们... 我们还在想时髦一点的名字...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.62,0:20:05.99,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Any suggestions?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你有没有建议?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.24,0:20:09.72,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}请稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:10.94,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:13.51,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, come on in. Lovely, oops...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}欢迎 请进 很好 哎呦...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:17.90,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Splendid! Splendid!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}很不错! 很不错!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:22.41,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Marvelous! Lovely lovely!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}真是不可思议! 很好很好!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.12,0:20:25.80,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- How are you?  - Very good, my dear.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 你还好吗?  - 我很好 亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.93,0:20:27.27,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,OK.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.54,0:20:33.14,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, uh... first of all, many thanks for taking part in this enterprise\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这个 呃... 首先 非常感谢各位参与此次的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.14,0:20:35.78,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,which I'm sure will go off flawlessly.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我相信一定会完美完成任务
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.86,0:20:38.07,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,These lovely passport and tickets\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这些护照和机票呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.07,0:20:41.57,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,will enable you to return home in the next 24 hours.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}可以让你在接下来的二十四小时内重返家园
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.77,0:20:45.63,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, upon arrival, you'll be taken in hand by our people\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那么 当你到达的时候 会有我们的人接应你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.63,0:20:48.53,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,so that we might recover our merchandise\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这样我们才可以收回我们的货
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.53,0:20:52.81,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,and you might re-discover the freedom which you so richly deserve.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}而你们则可以重新获得那千辛万苦挣来的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.81,0:20:57.68,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I don't need to remind you but, for any of those who may be tempted to\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}相信你们无需提醒 不过你们之中那些试图
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.68,0:21:02.61,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,warn or turn themselves in to the authorities,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}警告或者把自己交给警方的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.61,0:21:09.58,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,we have the names and addresses of the families of every one of you down to the distant cousins.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们手上有你所有家属的姓名和住址 包括你的三姑六婆八大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:15.66,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,So, we rely therefore, on your complete discretion.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}所以我们相信你们会慎重行事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.75,0:21:17.11,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, anyway, uh...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}很好 那么 呃...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.37,0:21:22.03,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,gentleman, madam, allow me to be the first to wish you\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}先生们 和女士 请让我作为第一个祝福你们的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.38,0:21:23.87,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,bon voyage!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一路顺风!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:30.46,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}哎呦!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.47,0:21:34.54,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,You gonna sell this?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你们要卖这东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.55,0:21:36.65,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid it's our business model.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}恐怕这就是我们的商业模式
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.20,0:21:44.51,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,For primitive beings like us, life seems to only have one single purpose.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}对于我们这种原始生物来说 生命似乎只有一个目的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.59,0:21:46.13,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Gaining time.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}获得时间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:51.14,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,And its going through time, seems to be also the only\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}而花费时间 似乎也正是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.14,0:21:53.85,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,real purpose of each of the cell in our bodies.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们体内每个细胞的真正和唯一的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.21,0:21:56.83,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,To achieve that aim, the mass of the cells\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}为了达到这个目标 那堆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.93,0:22:00.00,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,that make up earthworm and human beings\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}能组成包括蚯蚓和人类的细胞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.01,0:22:02.80,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,has only 2 solutions:\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}只有两种方法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.85,0:22:04.65,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,be immortal...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}长生不老...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.87,0:22:06.80,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,or to reproduce.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}或是繁衍后代
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.33,0:22:11.46,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,If its habitat is not sufficiently favourable or nurturing,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}若它们的栖息之地不适合繁殖后代
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.80,0:22:21.15,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,the cell will choose immortality.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}细胞则会选择长生不老
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.33,0:22:25.88,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, self-sufficiency and self-management.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}换句话说 自给自足以及自主管理
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.96,0:22:29.44,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, if the habitat is favourable,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}另一方面 若栖息之地及其有利
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.44,0:22:36.46,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,they will choose to reproduce.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}它们会选择繁殖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.81,0:22:48.09,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,That way, when they die,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这样一来 它们死的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.10,0:22:51.34,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,they hand down essential information and knowledge to the next cell\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}会传递必要的信息和知识给下一个细胞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.44,0:22:54.77,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,which hands it down to the next cell and so on.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}然后再传递给下一个细胞 以此类推
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.44,0:23:08.77,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, knowledge and learning\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}因此 知识和学问
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.88,0:23:11.86,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,are handed down through time.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}都是通过时间而传承的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.50,0:23:15.66,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, OK, keep calm...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好 好 保持冷静...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.77,0:23:18.06,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to wait, just play for time...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你必须等待 拖延时间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.11,0:23:20.65,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have time to think it through on the plane... just take the flight,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}在飞机上你会有时间想办法的... 先上飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.81,0:23:22.69,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,take the flight, get out of here.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}先上飞机 离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.85,0:23:25.36,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the main thing right now, just save time.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这是最主要的 争取时间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.41,0:23:28.35,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try anything, keep your cool, you're alive...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}什么都别干 保持冷静 你还活着...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.44,0:23:31.10,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,you're alive... you're alive, that's all that matters.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你还活着... 你还活着 只有这是重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.11,0:23:33.84,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait, save time.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}等待 争取时间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.00,0:23:36.30,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Save time.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}争取时间
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.62,0:24:10.84,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not in the mood.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}老娘我没心情
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.23,0:26:10.27,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's imagine for a few moments\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们稍微设想一下
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.27,0:26:13.93,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,what our life would be like if we could access, let's say,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}要是可以启用我们大脑的百分之二十的话
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.07,0:26:17.26,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,20 % of our brains' capacity.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们的生命会是什么样子
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.41,0:26:22.03,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,This first stage would give us access to and control\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这第一阶段会使我们能够了解并控制
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.11,0:26:23.88,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,of our own body.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.90,0:26:25.93,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- Sir.  - Yes?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 先生  - 请说?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.22,0:26:27.85,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Has it been proven scientifically?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这被科学证实了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.85,0:26:31.70,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, for the moment, it's just hypothesis, I confess.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}哦 目前来说 我承认这只是假设
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.70,0:26:33.83,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you think about it,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但是你想想看
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.83,0:26:38.66,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,it's troubling to realize that the Greeks, the Egyptians and the Indians\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}早在显微镜被发明几百年前 古埃及人 古希腊人和古印度人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.69,0:26:43.46,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,had notion of "cells" centuries before the invention of the microscope.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就意识到了"细胞"的存在 这是个让人不安的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.48,0:26:45.44,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,And what to say about Darwin\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}再看看达尔文
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.44,0:26:49.60,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,whom everybody took for a fool when he put forward his Theory of Evolution.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}当他提出进化论的时候 他遭到了所有人的嘲笑
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.66,0:26:52.87,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,It's up to us to push the rules and laws\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如今需要我们来有所突破
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.22,0:26:56.39,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,and go from "evolution" to "revolution".\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}从"进化"走向"革命"
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.51,0:27:01.40,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,100 billion neurons per human,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}平均每人有一千亿个神经元
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.44,0:27:04.30,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,of which only 15% are activated.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}其中被运用的只有15%
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.33,0:27:09.22,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,There're more connections in the human body than there're stars in the galaxy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}人体内各部分之间的联系比银河中的恒星还要多
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.66,0:27:13.73,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,We possess a gigantic network of information\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们拥有一个无比庞大的信息网络
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.73,0:27:16.23,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,to which we've almost no access.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但是我们对它仍几乎一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.08,0:27:19.39,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- Sir!  - Yes?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 先生!  - 请说?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.66,0:27:21.45,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,And what would be the next stage?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那下一阶段呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.45,0:27:25.01,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the next stage would probably be control of other people.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}嗯 在下一阶段很可能会是控制他人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.77,0:27:30.66,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,But for that, we will need to access at least 40% of our brains' capacity.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但是要做到这一点 我们需要至少能使用大脑的百分之四十
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.11,0:27:34.39,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,And after control of ourselves and others,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}在能控制自己和他人之后
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.55,0:27:37.08,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,come control of matter.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就是控制物质
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.11,0:27:41.18,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,But now we're entering the realm of science fiction.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但是这就完全是科幻小说了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.22,0:27:45.07,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,And we don't know anything more than a dog who watches the moon.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}对此 我们就像是犬狗望月一样一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.48,0:27:47.16,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- Excuse me, sir.  - Yes.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 打扰下 先生  - 请说
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.33,0:27:50.38,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,But what would happen if for some reason we ignore\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如果有人能使用其大脑百分之百的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.77,0:27:54.48,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,somebody unlock 100% of the celebral capacity?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那会是怎样的?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.02,0:27:57.41,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,100%?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}百分之百吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.67,0:27:58.40,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.55,0:28:03.34,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I've no idea.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我真不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.40,0:29:36.23,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}嘿!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.28,0:30:49.47,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hey, you speak English?  - No. No. No.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 嘿 你会说英语吗?  - 不 不 不
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.27,0:30:52.02,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- You speak English? - Yes. Yes.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 你会说英语吗?  - 会 会
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.12,0:30:54.41,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- Take me to the hospital now.  - Hospital?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 马上送我去医院  - 医院?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.57,0:31:45.56,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hospital.  - Wait for me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 医院  - 在这等我
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.69,0:32:34.28,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, hello?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}小姐 你好?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.78,0:32:37.78,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, miss!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}嘿 小姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.86,0:32:40.01,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I need help, it's urgent.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我需要帮助 很紧急
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.24,0:32:42.33,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot be in here. We're operating.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你不能进来 我们在做手术
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.33,0:32:44.41,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, get out!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}请你出去!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.91,0:33:05.33,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't be able to save him anyway.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你们根本救不了他
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.44,0:33:08.35,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Tumour already invaded the cortext and right side of his spine.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}肿瘤已经长到了他的大脑皮层和脊柱右侧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.34,0:33:13.79,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody put a bag of drug in me. I need you to remove it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有人在我身体里放了一袋毒品 我要你把它拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.00,0:33:15.37,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,It's leaking.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}它漏了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.13,0:33:19.47,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it now.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}现在就做
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.78,0:33:23.10,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. I'll just administer local anaethestic...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好 我先给你局部麻醉...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.20,0:33:24.48,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.83,0:33:27.90,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, I... okay.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好吧 我.... 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.33,0:33:32.08,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, please. Put the gun down.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}请冷静下 把枪放下来
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.40,0:33:35.88,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going to... examine, OK?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我先... 检查一下 好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.03,0:33:41.04,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- Do you mind?  - No.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 介意我用一下吗?  - 不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.09,0:33:51.95,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hello?  - Mom?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 你好?  - 妈?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.95,0:33:54.26,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lucy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}嘿 露西
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.26,0:33:56.56,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Baby, it's great to hear from you\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}宝贝 你打电话来我真开心
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.66,0:33:58.16,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,but what time is it over there?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你那里现在是几点?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.62,0:34:01.96,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. It's night.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不知道 是晚上了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.96,0:34:04.11,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a sec', let me get rid of the other line.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}等一下 先让我把另一通电话挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.11,0:34:07.12,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go inside.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我要开始取了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.12,0:34:09.86,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back, you're not partying too much, are you?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我回来了 你没有成天出去聚会吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.86,0:34:12.71,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,You promised me you'll look after yourself.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你答应过我会照顾好自己
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.77,0:34:15.68,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to, Mommy, I'm trying to.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我努力 妈妈 我努力
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.68,0:34:19.43,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, thanks for calling out of the blue like this.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好吧 谢谢你能意外地打电话回来
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.81,0:34:21.60,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father is gonna be sad he missed you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你父亲错过了你的电话 肯定很难过
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.79,0:34:26.14,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't home from the gym yet. Usually you call us in the morning.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他去了健身房还没回来 你一般都是早上打给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.15,0:34:28.67,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- Mom...  - Yes?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 妈...  - 嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.82,0:34:30.63,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel everything.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我感受到了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.44,0:34:32.98,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, sweatie?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你说什么 亲爱的?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.28,0:34:37.03,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Space,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}空间
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.88,0:34:39.27,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,the air,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}空气
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.33,0:34:45.10,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,the vibrations,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}振动
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.66,0:34:48.20,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,the people.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}还有人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.50,0:34:52.51,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel the gravity.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我能感觉到重力
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.33,0:34:56.88,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel the rotation of the Earth.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我能感觉到地球的转动
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.77,0:35:00.96,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,The heat leaving my body,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}身体的热量在消失
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.19,0:35:04.19,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,the blood in my veins,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}血管里的血液在流动
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.88,0:35:07.86,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel my brain.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我能感受到我的大脑
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.50,0:35:11.93,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,The deepest parts of my memory.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我记忆的最深处
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.19,0:35:16.21,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweatie, we've a bad connection, I can't hear you so well.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}亲爱的 信号不好 我听不太清你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.25,0:35:18.22,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say about "memory"?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你说"记忆"怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.48,0:35:24.69,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,The pain in my mouth, when I had braces, I ...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}当我带上牙箍时 嘴里的疼痛 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.77,0:35:30.07,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I can remember the feeling of your hand on my forehead when I ran a fever.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我记起我发烧时 你手摸我额头的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.22,0:35:34.31,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember stroking the cat. It was so soft.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我记得摸到猫的感觉 它真的很软
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.31,0:35:37.33,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,A cat? What cat, honey?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}猫? 什么猫 宝贝?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.87,0:35:40.74,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Siamese with blue eye and a broken tail.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}蓝眼睛 断了尾巴的那只暹罗猫
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.77,0:35:43.46,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweatie, you can't possibly remember that.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}亲爱的 你不可能还记得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.53,0:35:45.38,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,You were barely a year old.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你那时候只有一岁大
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.23,0:35:52.37,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember the days of your milk in my mouth,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我记得吃奶的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.43,0:35:54.89,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,the room,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那个房间
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.80,0:35:57.35,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,the liquid...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}乳汁...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.73,0:36:03.18,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweatie, what are you talking about?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}亲爱的 你在说些什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.15,0:36:08.70,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanna tell you that I love you, Mom and Dad...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我想告诉你我爱你们 爸妈...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.09,0:36:10.55,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweatie...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}亲爱的...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.80,0:36:13.16,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,And I wanna thank you for the...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我想谢谢你们 因为...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.16,0:36:17.19,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,thousand kisses that I can still feel on my face...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你们无数次吻在我脸上的感觉我仍感受得到...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.25,0:36:22.23,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Mom.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我爱你 妈
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.23,0:36:24.87,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you too, sweatie,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我也爱你 亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.88,0:36:27.14,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,more than anything in the world.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}胜过世间任何东西
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.98,0:36:37.49,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,How much is left?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}还剩多少?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.48,0:36:40.08,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,500 grams?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}五百克?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.99,0:36:44.16,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,And how long will it take for my body to eliminate the rest of it?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我身体还需要多少时间把其余的代谢掉?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.11,0:36:50.04,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,To answer that, I need to know what it is.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}要回答这个问题 我得知道这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.39,0:36:51.48,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,May I?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.58,0:36:52.65,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.69,0:36:55.34,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,CPH4.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是CPH4
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.00,0:37:00.42,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me about it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.44,0:37:06.73,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Pregnant women manufacture CPH4 in the sixth week of pregnancy,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}孕妇会在怀孕第六周的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.79,0:37:09.41,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,in tiny quantities.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}分泌微量的CPH4
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.41,0:37:14.05,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,For a baby, it packs the power of an atomic bomb.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这给婴儿带来了相当于一颗原子弹的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.25,0:37:19.51,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,It's what gives the foetus the necessary energy to form all the bones in its body.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这是胎儿生成骨骼结构所必需的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.86,0:37:22.59,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard they tried to make a synthetic version of it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我听说有人试图人工合成
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.69,0:37:25.19,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't realize that they succeeded.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没想到他们成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.71,0:37:28.30,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,If it really is CPH4,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如果这真是CPH4
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.40,0:37:31.65,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,in this quantity, I'm amazed you're still alive.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}以这个量来说 我真惊讶你竟然还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.61,0:37:34.18,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Not for long.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}活不了多久
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.81,0:39:43.40,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Learning is always a painful process.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}学习总是痛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.77,0:39:46.87,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Like when you're little, your bones are growing and you ached all over.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就像你小的时候 你会因骨骼生长而全身疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.22,0:39:51.28,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you believe I can remember the sound of my own bones growing?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你相信我能记得自己骨骼生长的声音吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.54,0:39:55.28,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this grinding under the skin.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}像这皮肤下磨得吱吱的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.33,0:39:57.02,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is different now.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}现在一切都不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.05,0:40:01.44,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Like... sound of music that I can understand, like fluids...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就比如... 我能理解音乐 就像流水...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.17,0:40:05.74,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,It's funny I used to be so concerned with\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有趣的是我曾经满脑子想着
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.90,0:40:09.55,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,who I was and what I wanted to be, and...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我是谁 我要成为什么样的人 还有...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.91,0:40:14.68,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,now I've access to the furthest reaches of my brain, I see things clearly and realize\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}现在我能感受到我脑海的最深处 我看待事情清晰了 也明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.68,0:40:17.79,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,what make us "us", it's primitive.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}"我们"成为如今这样是有其原始原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.79,0:40:20.55,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all obstacles.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}它们都是障碍物
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.30,0:40:22.95,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that make any sense?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你能明白吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.00,0:40:26.34,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this pain you're experiencing...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就像你正在遭受的痛苦...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.34,0:40:28.79,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,is blocking you from understanding.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}它使你无法理解其它事物
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.87,0:40:31.56,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,All you know now is pain.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你知道的只有疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.56,0:40:33.29,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all you know, pain.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你只知道疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.33,0:40:38.63,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the others?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}其他人在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.94,0:40:41.82,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,The others carrying the drugs. I need the rest of it\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}其他带着毒品的人 我需要剩下的毒品
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.90,0:40:43.70,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,for medicinal purposes.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}作医疗用途
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.12,0:41:15.26,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Berlin.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}柏林
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.71,0:41:21.70,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Paris.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}巴黎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.37,0:41:29.45,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Rome.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}罗马
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.99,0:41:36.57,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for sharing.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谢谢你的分享
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.16,0:41:53.09,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- Oh, good evening, Professor.  - I sweared I'll be back.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 晚上好 教授  - 我说过我会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.92,0:41:55.53,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,You hadn't forget your dinner tonight?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你今晚没忘了用餐吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.57,0:41:58.00,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid so. I'm exhausted.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}恐怕是的 我累坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.00,0:42:00.00,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- Have a good rest.  - Thank you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 好好休息  - 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.75,0:42:08.76,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,You scared the shit out of me. You ring that bell like some nut bar!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你吓死我了 这门敲得跟个神经病一样!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.76,0:42:11.39,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I missed you!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我想你啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.61,0:42:14.83,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.93,0:42:17.49,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,You lose your key or something?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你丢了钥匙还是怎么?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.74,0:42:18.72,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.64,0:42:22.35,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- Can I borrow your laptop?  - Yeah, of course.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 我能借你笔记本用下吗?  - 好的 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.44,0:42:25.27,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,So I spent all day at this audition, awesome.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我去试镜试了一整天 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.44,0:42:30.70,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,They just have you standing around all day because they don't give a shit about your time, gabbing away in Chinese.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们满口中文 就让你在那站一整天 因为他们根本就不在乎你的时间重不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.80,0:42:33.46,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Who understand Chinese? I don't understand Chinese.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谁能听懂中文? 反正我是不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.74,0:42:35.91,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,And then they say they always gonna call\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们还说他们一定会有回信
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.05,0:42:38.15,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,and they never do. They don't even take your phone number.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但是从不回信 他们都不记你的手机号码
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.17,0:42:41.88,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,You know.Except this one guy, I bet he, uh...he's not Chinese.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你知道吧 除了一个男的 我觉着他... 他不是中国人
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.03,0:42:45.60,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,He works at the agency and he's cute... Oh my God, he's cute!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他在那儿工作 很帅... 天啊 他真帅!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.68,0:42:49.27,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, like, the cute in kinda way, like he has this thing...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你懂的 帅得很特别 有种特殊的魅力...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.27,0:42:51.58,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my God, his ass...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}天啊 他的屁股...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.88,0:42:53.33,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me get started on that!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们来说说这个!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.39,0:42:55.60,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,And you'll never gonna guess where he take me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你肯定猜不到他带我去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.69,0:43:01.05,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Four Seasons, Royal Suite, and we made love all night.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}四季酒店 皇家套房 我们一整晚都在滚床单
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.88,0:43:05.47,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I'm talking about myself. What's up? How's Richard?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}抱歉 光顾着说我了 你呢? 理查德怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.66,0:43:06.81,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,He's dead.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他死了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.84,0:43:09.74,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are crazy. I'm gonna take a shower.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你们真疯 我去冲个澡
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.41,0:43:23.61,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yes?  - Profesor Norman, my name is Lucy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 你好?  - 诺曼教授 我的名字叫露西
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.61,0:43:26.76,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just read all your research on the human's brain. We need to meet.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我看完了你有关人脑的所有研究 我们有必要见个面
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.22,0:43:30.91,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,All of my research?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我所有的研究?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.54,0:43:35.66,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm very flattered, young lady. But I find that hard to believe.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}真是受宠若惊 小姐 但是这让人难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.91,0:43:37.32,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I must have written no less than...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我可写了整整...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.32,0:43:41.94,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,6734 pages. I can recite them too all by heart if you wish.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}六千七百三十四页 我可以全部背出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.70,0:43:47.54,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you one of Emily's friends?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你是艾米丽的朋友吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.40,0:43:51.66,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,This sounds like one of her silly jokes. Is she there with you?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这听起来真像她开的玩笑 她和你在一起吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.71,0:43:53.35,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm on my own.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不 只有我一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.66,0:43:58.23,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- Who are you?  - I just told you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 你是谁?  - 我刚告诉过你
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.66,0:44:03.24,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, right? Yes, sorry.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}露西 是吗? 是的 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.24,0:44:05.62,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I read your theory on the use of the brain's capacity.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我看了你有关大脑使用的理论
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.86,0:44:08.33,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little rudimentary but you're on the right track.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}还有些粗糙 不过方向是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.66,0:44:10.91,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}哦 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.01,0:44:14.13,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, my cells are reproducing at a phenomenal speed,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}教授 我的细胞正在以惊人的速度再生
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.23,0:44:15.59,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,several millions per second,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}每秒几百万个
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.79,0:44:19.05,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm having trouble precisely evaluating the time of my death\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我也无法精确估算我剩下的寿命
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.05,0:44:21.62,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,but I doubt it'll last more than 24 hours.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但是我觉得不会超过二十四小时
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.62,0:44:23.11,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你在说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.12,0:44:26.36,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm saying is that your theory is not a theory.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我是说你的理论不只是理论
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.36,0:44:30.55,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I absorbed a large quatity of synthetic CPH4\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我吸收了大量人工合成的CPH4
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.77,0:44:33.94,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,that would allow me to use 100% of my celebral capacity.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}可以让我百分之百地运用我的大脑
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.00,0:44:37.40,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now I'm at 28% and which you wrote is true.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}现在我的使用率到了百分之二十八 你写的是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.40,0:44:41.44,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Once the brain reaches 20% , it opens up and expands the rest\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一旦大脑使用了百分之二十 它会整个打开
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.44,0:44:43.10,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,and there are no more obstacles.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不会再有阻碍
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.11,0:44:46.40,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,They fall away like dominos. I'm colonizing my own brain.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就像多米诺骨牌倒下一样 我正在开拓我的大脑
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.68,0:44:53.71,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... well... I don't know... what to... say.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}呃... 好吧... 我不知道... 该说... 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.66,0:44:59.58,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true, I've... I've been working on this theory for over 20 years but it's...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}真的 我... 我研究这个理论超过二十年了 但是它...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.68,0:45:05.39,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,it's only... all ever been hypothesis and research ideas.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}它只是... 只是假设和研究想法
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.40,0:45:08.49,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I never thought anyone would...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我... 我从没想过有人能...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.88,0:45:12.00,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,You can control your own metabolism?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你可以控制自己的新陈代谢吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.01,0:45:13.19,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.49,0:45:16.61,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,And I can start to control other people's bodies.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}然后我开始能够控制他人的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.61,0:45:20.26,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Also I can control magnetic and electric waves and...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我也能控制磁力 电波还有...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.43,0:45:23.76,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,not all of them, just... the most basic.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不是全部 只是... 最基本的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.12,0:45:25.38,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Television.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}电视
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.22,0:45:27.48,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Telephone.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}电话
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.66,0:45:30.78,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Radio.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}收音机
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.35,0:45:35.71,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这太神奇了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.04,0:45:40.00,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel pain,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我感受不到痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.33,0:45:42.65,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,fear,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.59,0:45:44.96,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,desire.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.62,0:45:49.72,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like all things that make us human are fading away.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就好像所有人类的特征都在慢慢消失
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.55,0:45:55.87,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like the less human I feel,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}当我越发感觉不像人类的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.38,0:46:00.17,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,all these knowledge about... everything,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}所有的知识... 关于世界万物的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.17,0:46:03.62,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Quantum Physics, Applied Mathemathics,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}量子物理 应用数学
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.88,0:46:07.65,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,the infinite capacity of the cell's nucleus,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}细胞核的无限容量
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.16,0:46:11.26,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,they're all exploding inside my brain, all these knowledge...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}它们都涌向我的大脑 所有的知识...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.33,0:46:14.00,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what to do with it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不知道该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.73,0:46:19.92,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're asking me... what to do...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如果你是在问我... 该怎么做...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.97,0:46:30.28,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你知道...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.93,0:46:34.64,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think about\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你想想看
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.44,0:46:37.95,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,the very nature of life...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}生命的本源...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.31,0:46:41.20,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, from the very begining...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我的意思是 生命的最初...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.40,0:46:48.10,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,The development of the first cell... divided into two cells.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}第一个细胞的生长... 分裂成两个细胞
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.02,0:46:52.56,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,This whole purpose of life has been\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}生命的全部意义在于
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.71,0:46:57.17,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,passed on what was learned.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}传承已有的知识
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.63,0:47:01.30,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no higher purpose.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没有更崇高的意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.44,0:47:06.19,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,So if you're asking me what to do with all these knowledge you're accumalating, I'd say...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}所以如果你问我对于你这些正在不断增长的知识 你应该怎么做 我会说
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.55,0:47:10.00,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,pass it on.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}将它延续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.10,0:47:16.59,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like any simple cell,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就像任何一个简单的细胞一样
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.91,0:47:18.58,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,going through time.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}通过时间传承
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.88,0:47:21.14,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Time?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}时间?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.52,0:47:23.95,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的 当然
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.74,0:47:28.36,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be at your door in 12 hours.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我会在十二小时之内到你那里
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.37,0:47:39.16,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- You leaving?  - Yes.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 你要走了?   - 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.16,0:47:44.73,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- What is this?  - A prescription.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 这是什么?  - 一个处方
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.93,0:47:47.07,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Since when did you start writing Chinese?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你什么时候开始会写中文了?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.26,0:47:50.32,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- Since an hour ago.  - Lucy, I don't understand any of this.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 一小时前  - 露西 我一个字都看不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.32,0:47:54.73,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Your kidneys aren't functioning efficiently. Your liver is failing. You need to make some lifestyle changes.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你的肾功能不太好 你的肝脏功能也在减弱 你得改变你的生活方式
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.83,0:47:57.72,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this medication. Work out. Eat organic.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}吃这个药 多锻炼 吃些有机食物
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.77,0:47:59.13,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be OK.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.63,0:48:09.67,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night, at 11 p.m., a woman shot a patient dead.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}昨晚十一点 一名女子枪杀了一位病人
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.93,0:48:40.90,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Del Rio.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我是德·里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.55,0:48:52.83,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hello ?  - Yes, I've important imformation about a group of drug traffickers.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 你好?  - 我有关于大型贩毒团伙的重要信息
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.83,0:48:55.24,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to speak with someone in position of authority.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我要跟当局说话
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.29,0:49:00.03,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah-hah, you're very lucky. There's no one with more authority in this office than me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}啊哈 你很幸运 这办公室里没人职位比我高了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.06,0:49:02.24,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,But let's start with the begining. What's your name?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}从头开始吧 你叫什么名字?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.25,0:49:06.00,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, Pierre Del Rio, get off your desk, sit in your chair,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}听着 皮埃尔·德·里奥 离开桌子 坐回椅子上
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.11,0:49:09.05,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,pick up the red pen to your left and take down everything I say.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}拿起你左手边的红色笔 记下我要说的每个字
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.55,0:49:18.71,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,There're no cameras, hurry up. I've no time to waste.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没有摄像头 快点 我没时间浪费了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.94,0:49:27.95,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.97,0:49:31.33,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be sending you details of three people about to arrive in Europe.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有三个人即将抵达欧洲 我要告诉你他们的详细信息
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.33,0:49:35.45,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Each one is carrying a kilo of drugs. I need you to arrest them and collect the substance.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们每人都携带了一千克毒品 我要你逮捕他们 拿到毒品
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.46,0:49:36.63,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll need it later.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我稍后有用
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.70,0:49:39.53,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,What form of these drugs in? Bars? Capsules?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}什么样的毒品? 条状? 还是装在胶囊里?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.68,0:49:43.57,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Powder, hidden in plastic pouches inside their intestines.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}粉末 用塑料袋装着 藏在他们腹内
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.66,0:49:44.65,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.66,0:49:47.90,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure to be careful when you remove them. The product is very powerful.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}取走的时候一定要小心 那粉末威力很大
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.52,0:49:55.67,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.19,0:49:58.58,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}看到了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.70,0:49:59.73,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.11,0:50:01.33,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}很好
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.12,0:50:03.55,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我可指望你了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.31,0:51:37.48,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好的 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.18,0:51:56.03,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Del Rio.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我是德·里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.46,0:51:58.67,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for calling me back.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谢谢你回电话给我
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.95,0:52:00.62,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,We got the third guy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们抓到第三个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.33,0:52:03.42,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks very much. I'll send you the paper work with the transfer.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}非常感谢 我把交接犯罪分子文件发给你
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.48,0:52:05.17,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}再见
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.75,0:52:16.31,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen, we're now beginning our descend to Paris-Charles de Gaulle.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}女士们 先生们 飞机即将降落于巴黎戴高乐机场
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.77,0:52:27.34,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, I've to ask you to put away your computer now.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}女士 现在需要请您关闭电脑
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.35,0:52:29.08,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,You should wipe your nose.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你该擦擦鼻子
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.21,0:52:31.85,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- Excuse me?  - May I have a glass of champagne?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 什么?  - 可以给我一杯香槟吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.44,0:52:34.54,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, yes, of course.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}嗯 好的 当然
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.86,0:52:55.89,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, your champagne.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}女士 您的香槟
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.13,0:52:58.50,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.76,0:53:02.45,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry but... uh, you really need to close your table now.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}很抱歉打扰... 但是 你必须收起小桌板了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.04,0:53:04.22,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.07,0:53:15.36,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,To knowledge.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}敬知识
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.53,0:53:29.96,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,If the habitat is not sufficiently favorable or nurturing...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}若它们的栖息之地不适合繁殖后代...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.21,0:53:41.03,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,the cell will choose immortality.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}细胞会选择长生不老
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.03,0:53:50.39,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,In another word, self-sufficiency and self-management.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}换句话来说 自给自足以及自主管理
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.59,0:54:08.03,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,No, miss, miss.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不 女士 女士
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.05,0:54:11.57,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,You must remain seated.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}您必须回到座椅上
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.94,0:54:13.12,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, stop!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}女士 站住!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.20,0:54:19.27,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}女士...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.55,0:54:24.36,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, open the door! You really have to go back to your seat! Miss!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}女士 打开门! 您必须回到您的座椅上! 女士!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.93,0:54:26.97,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to land soon, please, open the door!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们马上要降落了 请您开门!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.71,0:54:30.86,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, say something, are you okay?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}说话啊 您还好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.88,0:54:31.91,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}女士?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.04,0:54:34.92,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}女士!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.43,0:54:38.20,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, please open the door!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}女士 请开门!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.50,0:54:44.24,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Do something, help me open!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}快帮忙 帮我打开!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.85,0:54:56.44,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me! Open the door!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}回答我! 开门!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.51,0:55:09.20,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss? Are you okay? Say something!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}女士? 您还好吗? 说句话啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.40,0:56:24.73,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, don't move!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}女士 不要动!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.06,0:56:28.77,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- I need to talk to you alone.  - And I need you to put your hands up, please.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 我要跟你单独谈谈  - 我要你举起双手
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.96,0:56:51.55,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get the packets?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你拿到那几袋东西了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.22,0:56:54.36,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.04,0:56:57.55,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- Where're they?  - They're safe.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 在哪里?  - 一个安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.23,0:57:00.44,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, in Paris.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就在巴黎
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.54,0:57:02.39,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be safer in my hands.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}交给我更安全
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.26,0:57:33.68,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, as a cop, we see some pretty weird shit\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你知道 作为警察 怪事我见过一些
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.49,0:57:36.11,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,but I've to be honest with you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}可是坦白地说
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.27,0:57:38.70,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,What you did back there, that freaked me out.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你刚在那的举动 把我吓坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.47,0:57:41.70,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,To put everyone to sleep like that,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}让所有人一下昏睡过去
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.72,0:57:43.75,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,do I need to be worried?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我该担心吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.04,0:57:45.11,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,No.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不用
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.51,0:57:47.43,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.29,0:58:10.53,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mind?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你介意吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.47,0:58:12.54,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,No.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.10,0:58:33.33,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- What's that?  - Korean, I'm going to drive.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 这是什么?  - 韩语 我来开车
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.96,0:58:36.84,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey! Hey! No! No! No! This is a police car!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}嘿! 嘿! 嘿! 不! 不! 不! 这是警车!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.90,0:58:39.76,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't! No, this is not possible, lady.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你不能这么做! 不 不能这样 女士
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.76,0:58:41.27,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a police car!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这是警车!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.40,0:58:44.75,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, OK.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好的 好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.36,0:59:00.86,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, sir, excuse me, sir.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}先生 先生 很抱歉 先生
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.86,0:59:02.24,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to talk to somebody.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我有话要说
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.36,0:59:07.02,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I'm a German citizen and I demand us a lawyer.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}听着 我是德国公民 我要见律师
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.22,0:59:40.77,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you always drive like that?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你平时都这么开车吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.77,0:59:42.44,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I never driven before.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我以前没开过车
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.73,0:59:43.82,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Great.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}真好
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.56,0:59:52.04,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hey, this is one way!  - We're late.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 嘿 这是单行道!  - 我们要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.83,1:00:15.52,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I would rather be late than dead.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}嘿 迟到总比没命好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.52,1:00:16.98,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,We never really die.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们不会死的
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.77,1:01:09.70,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sir, I don't agree...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}抱歉 先生 我不同意...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.55,1:01:18.84,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine, fine.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我没意见
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.53,1:01:33.03,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to tell them to stop following us.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我要告诉他们别跟着我们
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.04,1:01:34.19,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不用麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.93,1:02:58.24,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me the case.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}把箱子给我
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.88,1:04:09.93,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Open it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}打开
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.65,1:04:24.85,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们走
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.85,1:04:27.52,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure I could be of any help for you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我觉得我什么都帮不到你
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.08,1:04:33.50,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you are.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不 你帮得到
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.21,1:04:35.31,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,What for?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}怎么帮?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.77,1:04:43.34,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,A reminder.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}提醒我
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.06,1:04:45.48,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}可以走了吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.66,1:05:14.94,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we going?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们去哪里?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.94,1:05:16.94,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Take the first left.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}第一个路口左转
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.73,1:05:19.95,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好的
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.06,1:05:43.29,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- Professor?  - Thanks.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 教授?  - 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.29,1:05:44.92,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yes?  - Lucy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 你好?  - 我是露西
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.21,1:05:46.67,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,It's her, it's her.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是她 她打来了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.77,1:05:49.45,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you, you're in Paris?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}嘿 你好 你在巴黎?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.46,1:05:50.51,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的 我到了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.51,1:05:52.40,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, good, excellant.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}很好 很好 太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.63,1:05:57.42,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,So, look, I'm no longer at the hotel now, uh, I've come to the university\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}听着 我已经离开酒店了 来大学里了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.42,1:06:02.03,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,where I've taken the liberty of calling and gathering a few of my colleagues to discuss your case.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我已经请来几位同事一起讨论你的事情了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.04,1:06:05.40,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Top men in their field and um... very trustworthy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们都是各自领域的精英... 可以信赖
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.46,1:06:06.70,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I trust you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我相信你
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.80,1:06:10.30,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you. So, do you think you can meet us here at the university?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}噢 谢谢 那我们可以在学校见吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.02,1:06:18.45,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm, uh...I'm very pleased to meet you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我... 我很高兴见到你
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.45,1:06:20.16,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Likewise.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我也是
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.16,1:06:22.43,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- Captain Del Rio.  - How do you do?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 我是德·里奥警长  - 你好
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.43,1:06:27.17,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Let... let me introduce you to my colleagues.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我... 介绍同事给你认识
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.37,1:06:29.84,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Professor Cartier, neuro surgeon.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这位是卡帝亚教授 脑外科医生
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.84,1:06:31.57,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- Professor...  - I know who everyone is.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 教授...  - 所有人我都认识
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.29,1:06:34.75,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, of course.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}啊 当然
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.77,1:06:39.11,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, gentlemen, this is Lucy, the first woman to...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}嗯 先生们 这位是露西 第一个女人...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.26,1:06:42.55,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean... like I mentioned earlier...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我想说... 我之前有介绍...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.88,1:06:46.50,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Lucy has for reasons, remains a mystery to me,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}露西小姐 因为某种对我来说还是个迷的原因
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.50,1:06:50.33,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,unlocked certain portion of her brain\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}她脑部的某些区域得到开发
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.33,1:06:51.82,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,that offered access\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}可以进入
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.88,1:06:55.93,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,to... previously unexplored celebral zones.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们... 未知的某些领域
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.66,1:06:59.55,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,She has abilities.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}她有超能力
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.66,1:07:01.28,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you give us an example?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}能给我们示范下吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.37,1:07:04.73,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Your daughter, Gabriel, aged 6, died in a car accident.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你的女儿 盖布里埃尔 六岁时死于车祸
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.80,1:07:07.06,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a blue car, leather seats...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是辆蓝色轿车 皮座椅...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.16,1:07:09.52,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,plastic bird hanging from the rear view mirror.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}后视镜上有只塑料小鸟挂饰
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.87,1:07:52.82,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,There're men coming here, can you secure the room?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有人要来了 你能守住这里吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.83,1:07:55.10,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,- I need to stay focus.  - Sure.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 我需要集中注意力  - 好的
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.72,1:08:02.10,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Speed it up.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}快点
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.17,1:08:14.39,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you manage to access all these information?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你如何掌握这些信息的?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.39,1:08:16.21,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Electrical impulses...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}电子脉冲...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.22,1:08:19.25,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Every cell knows and talks to every other cell.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}每个细胞都熟悉其他的细胞 并且相互交流
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.30,1:08:22.43,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,They exchange a thousand bits of information between them per second.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}彼此间每秒钟交换一千比特信息
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.63,1:08:25.99,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Cells group together, forming a giant web of communication\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}细胞们聚在一起 形成强大的通信网
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.24,1:08:28.04,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,which in turn forms matter.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}然后构成物质
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.01,1:08:32.09,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Cells get together, take on one form,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}细胞们聚在一起 组成形态
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.54,1:08:34.35,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,deform, reform,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}变形 再重新组合
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.55,1:08:36.75,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,makes no difference, it's all the same.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}本质上没什么不同 都是一样的
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.55,1:08:39.47,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Human considers themself unique.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}人类认为自己独一无二
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.48,1:08:43.01,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,So, they rooted their whole theory of existence on their uniqueness.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}所以他们将人类存在的所有理论都植根于独特上
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.19,1:08:46.35,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,"One"... is the unit of measure but it's not.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}"一"... 是衡量一切的标准 但其实不是
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.36,1:08:49.53,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,All social systems we put into place are mere "sketch".\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}所有的社交系统不过只是"草图"
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.54,1:08:52.10,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,1 + 1 = 2 That's all we learned.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一加一等于二 这是我们唯一知道的
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.30,1:08:55.11,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,But 1 + 1 has never equalled 2.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但一加一从来就不等于二
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.50,1:08:58.56,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,They're in fact, no numbers and no letters.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}事实上 没有所谓的数字或字母
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.56,1:09:02.06,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,We codify our existence to bring it down to human size\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们把自己的存在用人类的概念去解释
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.06,1:09:04.10,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,to make it comprehensible.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}以便理解
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.11,1:09:09.04,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,We created the scale so that we can forget its unfathomable scale.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们创造了尺度 忘记其实一切变幻莫测
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.33,1:09:14.82,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,But if humans are not the unit of measure,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但如果人类不是衡量的标尺
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.06,1:09:17.96,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,and the world isn't governed by mathemathical laws,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}世界也不是由数学原理掌控的
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.02,1:09:20.64,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,what governs all that?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谁来掌控一切?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.36,1:09:24.48,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Form a car speeding down the road...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一辆车驶过路面...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.56,1:09:27.10,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,speed up the image infinitely\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}加速这幅画面无穷快
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.89,1:09:29.56,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,and the car disappears.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}车辆消失
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.54,1:09:35.80,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what proof do we have of its existence?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}所以 什么证明了我们的存在?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.81,1:09:38.14,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Time gives legitimacy to its existence.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}时间给我们存在合法性
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.15,1:09:41.26,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Time is the only true unit of meassure.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}时间是衡量一切的标准
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.74,1:09:44.70,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,It gives proof to the existence of matter.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}它证明物质的存在
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.00,1:09:46.27,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Without time,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没有时间
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.53,1:09:49.02,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,we don't exist.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们都不存在
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.43,1:09:57.05,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Time is "unity".\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}时间才是"个体"
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.28,1:10:13.33,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,We wouldn't be able to hold them for much longer.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们撑不了太久的
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.49,1:10:16.14,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to go then.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那开始吧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.19,1:10:32.14,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you need such huge doses?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你确定要这么大剂量?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.24,1:10:33.72,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid you won't survive.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我怕你承受不了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.72,1:10:37.91,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Some cells inside me will fight and defend their integrity to the very end.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我身体里的一些细胞会誓死捍卫它们的完整性
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.91,1:10:41.36,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to attain the last few percent, I've to force it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}为了开发最后一部分 我必须逼迫它们
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.72,1:10:44.13,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,To crack the cells open to their nucleus.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}击破细胞 打开细胞核
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.35,1:10:55.28,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,All these knowledge, Lucy...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这些知识 露西...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.33,1:11:00.32,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not even sure that mankind is ready for it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我甚至不确定人类能否接受
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.32,1:11:02.95,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,We're so driven by power and profit.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们被权势利益所驱使
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.33,1:11:05.37,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Given man's nature,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}鉴于人类本性
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.40,1:11:09.66,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,it might bring us only instability and chaos.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}也许这只会给我们带来动荡和混乱
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.86,1:11:16.29,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Ignorance brings chaos, not knowledge.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}无知才导致混乱 不是知识
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.44,1:11:19.53,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll build a computer and download all my knowledge in it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我会造一个电脑 把我所知的一切放在里面
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.76,1:11:22.55,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find a way for you to have access to it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我会想办法把它给你
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.29,1:11:24.38,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好的
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.95,1:11:28.32,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,I just hope, we'll be worthy of your sacrifice.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我希望你的牺牲是值得的
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.68,1:11:39.97,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody move!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不准动!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.23,1:11:59.12,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand English?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}能听懂英语吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.33,1:13:02.53,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,What is she doing?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}她在干吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.66,1:13:05.33,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,She's looking for energy and matter.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}她在寻找能量和物质
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.37,1:13:12.46,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,And she's trying to connect with our computers.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}还在尝试连接我们的电脑
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.93,1:14:17.94,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my God, what's happening?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}天啊 怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.49,1:14:30.23,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,What's she making?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}她在做什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.37,1:14:32.95,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,A new generation of computer, I presume.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我猜是新一代的计算机
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.49,1:21:04.55,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}嘿 说你呢!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.39,1:21:23.92,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, the computer, it's moving.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}看电脑 它在移动
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.29,1:21:51.56,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}嘿
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.35,1:21:53.47,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}她去哪里了?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.61,1:22:25.26,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Life was given to us a billion years ago.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}十亿年前 我们被赐予了生命
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.03,1:22:28.07,英上中下,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you know what to do with it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}现在你知道能用它做什么了
